6 pages, 5 figures; Figs. 2, 3 and 5 updated from re-analysis of data
  including UrQMD model predictions. Plotting error in Fig. 4 corrected;
  Accepted for publication in Phys. Rev. Lett

To appear in Journal of Data Science, Statistics, and Visualisation.
  The previous preprint version was titled "Interpretable Contrastive Learning
  for Networks" (arXiv:2005.12419v1)
